- [ ] Guard Rail metrics present

### Sprint Ready
- [ ] KRs quantified
- [ ] Dev spec document linked
- [ ] Baseline data secured

### Hypothesis Validation
- [ ] Before data collection complete
- [ ] Measurement period set
- [ ] Success/failure criteria clear

